<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:4.14px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">2)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:104.40px;top:4.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">道が  すぐ  わかりましたか。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:159.60px;top:20.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">せん せい</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:210.00px;top:20.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">くるま</span></div>
