<div style="position:absolute;left:104.40px;top:61.74px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">むずか</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:157.20px;top:61.74px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">きょく</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:228.00px;top:61.74px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">じょうず</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:280.80px;top:61.74px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">ひ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:65.34px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">3)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:104.40px;top:65.34px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">難しい</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:157.20px;top:65.34px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">曲なのに、上手に  弾けましたね。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:120.00px;top:82.14px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">はは</span></div>
